  [FiniteDimensional ùïú G] [FiniteDimensional ùïú H]:
  LinearMap.adjoint (swap_middle_tensor ùïú E F G H).toLinearMap
    = (swap_middle_tensor ùïú E F G H).symm.toLinearMap :=
